            h2.subtitle-1 Acupuncture
            p Acupuncture is a traditional Chinese medicine. It is used treat back pain, neck pain, and certain types of athritis. It also may help reduce or prevent headaches.
            h3.heading-1 How it Works
            p Acupuncture stimulates the nervous system, which causes a release chemicals that affect the muscles, spinal cord, and brain. This stimulates healing and reduces pain. Dispite a long history of use in the treatment of emotional, neurologic, enterologic, and gynecologic conditions, its value in these areas is unclear.
